NAME

Javascript::Menu - a module that builds Javascript + HTML menus.

DESCRIPTION

This module helps in creation of the Javascript, CSS and HTML required to produce a table-based menu. Special consideration has been given to i18n.

See the documentation for this module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Mandatory - NumberedTree.pm

Will warn of a missing dependency if you don't have NumberedTree::DBTree, but you can ignore that if you don't need it. If you do, you won't be able to use Javascript::Menu->readDB.

